    dc:description "FIGURE 38. Syringophiloidus glandarii (Fritsch), male (A–D). A, dorsal view; B, peritreme; C, genito-anal region; D, fan-like seta p’ of leg III. Female (E–I). E, peritreme, F, propodonotal setae ve; G, fan-like seta p’ of leg III; H, ventral view of opisthosoma; I, pseudanal setae ps1 and ps2. Scale bars: A = 100 µm; C, H = 50 µm; B, D–G, I = 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5289354/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

